msgstr "Sorotan keamanan"

#: templates/security.html:51
msgid "AES-256 encryption"
msgstr "Enkripsi AES-256"

#: templates/security.html:52
msgid "Zero-trust access"
msgstr "Akses zero-trust"

#: templates/security.html:53
msgid "Resilient backups"
msgstr "Cadangan yang tangguh"

#: templates/security.html:60
msgid "Defense in Depth"
msgstr "Pertahanan Berlapis"

#: templates/security.html:61
msgid "Multi-layered protection at every stage"
msgstr "Perlindungan berlapis di setiap tahap"

#: templates/security.html:62
msgid "We use overlapping controls so your payroll data stays protected in transit, at rest, and during access."
msgstr "Kami menggunakan kontrol yang tumpang tindih sehingga data penggajian Anda tetap terlindungi saat transit, saat diam, dan selama akses."

#: templates/security.html:67
msgid "Advanced encryption"
msgstr "Enkripsi lanjutan"

#: templates/security.html:68
msgid "AES-256 encryption protects sensitive data at rest and in transit, keeping it unreadable if intercepted."
msgstr "Enkripsi AES-256 melindungi data sensitif saat diam dan dalam transit, menjadikannya tidak terbaca jika dicegat."

#: templates/security.html:73
msgid "RBAC and MFA restrict access to only what each user needs — minimizing internal and accidental exposure risk."
msgstr "RBAC dan MFA membatasi akses hanya pada apa yang dibutuhkan setiap pengguna — meminimalkan risiko paparan internal dan tidak disengaja."

#: templates/security.html:77
msgid "Secure cloud infrastructure"
msgstr "Infrastruktur cloud yang aman"

#: templates/security.html:78
msgid "Hosted on mature cloud environments with real-time backups, mirrored regions, and resilient disaster recovery."
msgstr "Dihosting di lingkungan cloud yang matang dengan cadangan waktu nyata, wilayah cermin, dan pemulihan bencana yang tangguh."

#: templates/security.html:86
msgid "Access & Governance"
msgstr "Akses & Tata Kelola"

#: templates/security.html:87
msgid "Built to reduce risk and prevent mistakes"
msgstr "Dibangun untuk mengurangi risiko dan mencegah kesalahan"

#: templates/security.html:88
